The Job Auto-Complete Card allows your Interfaces to inform your ME Network that a performed recipe has been completed, §bregardless§f of whether the expected output has actually been crafted.

A possible use-case for this would be to pattern the "ingredient" blocks required to construct a LCR, and then use an §6Auto-Complete Card§f so that the craft does not hang. Now, you can order §aentire multiblocks§f from the comfort of your Terminal!
